      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, top, tail, peel then&nbsp;chop the <strong>carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into matchsticks</p>\r\n<p>Cut the <strong>baby corn</strong> into quarters</p>\r\n<p>Cut the <strong>green beans</strong> in half&nbsp;</p>",
