          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Separate the<strong> egg yolk<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> from the <strong>egg white<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>, discard the<strong> white<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>Combine the <strong>egg yolk<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> with the <strong>cornflour</strong>, a pinch of<strong> salt&nbsp;</strong>and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>milk </strong>&ndash;&nbsp;this is your <strong>batter</strong></p>\r\n<p>Add the<strong> diced chicken</strong> to the <strong>batter </strong>and&nbsp;give everything a good mix up</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
